title: The George R. R. Martin Podcast
description: Join the New York Times bestselling author of the epic A Song of Ice and Fire cycle, George R. R. Martin, for his very first podcast. In these eight episodes, George covers a range of topics from the birth of his acclaimed saga, to his experiences in Hollywood, to "weird stuff," and even reads an excerpt his new paperback novel A FEAST FOR CROWS.
